1
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:14,000
To connect to Microsoft Teams  
from the Session Details page,

2
00:00:14,100 --> 00:00:19,000
make sure Microsoft Teams  
is selected in the Connection Type box.

3
00:00:19,100 --> 00:00:23,000
Then click Connect.

4
00:00:24,100 --> 00:00:30,000
Your browser may display a dialogue  
telling you the page is trying

5
00:00:30,100 --> 00:00:32,000
to open the Microsoft Teams app.

6
00:00:32,100 --> 00:00:36,000
If you want to use Teams on the web,  
click Cancel.

7
00:00:36,100 --> 00:00:39,000
Otherwise, click Open.

8
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:43,900
You'll then be taken to the  
Join Conversation page.

9
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:48,000
This page offers three different options
to join the meeting.

10
00:00:48,100 --> 00:00:51,900
First, you can download  
the Microsoft Teams app.

11
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:56,000
After installation, the app  
will launch automatically.

12
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:01,000
Second, you can open  
Microsoft Teams in your browser.

13
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:07,000
Third, you can open the meeting  
in the app if it's already installed.

14
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:13,000
If it's your first time using Teams  
in the browser,

15
00:01:13,100 --> 00:01:22,000
click Allow when prompted  
to use your microphone and camera.

16
00:01:25,100 --> 00:01:30,000
You'll also have the option  
to dial in to a meeting.

17
00:01:30,100 --> 00:01:35,000
The Session Details page contains  
a link to dial-in numbers by country.

18
00:01:37,100 --> 00:01:44,000
To join by phone, make a note  
of the Conference ID.

19
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:48,500
It is made up of nine digits.

20
00:01:54,500 --> 00:02:01,000
For the best experience,  
sign in with your Learnlight account.

21
00:02:01,100 --> 00:02:06,900
Without signing in, browser options  
are limited.

22
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:10,000
To sign in, click the link  
at the bottom of the page

23
00:02:10,100 --> 00:02:12,000
before joining a meeting.

24
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:17,000
By signing in, the experience  
is similar to the desktop app.

25
00:02:17,100 --> 00:02:23,000
Please note: these features  
are not available in the browser:

26
00:02:23,100 --> 00:02:27,000
The option to change or blur  
your background,

27
00:02:27,100 --> 00:02:28,900
live captions,

28
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:31,000
and the back and forward arrows.
